@Kashim22 

That's correct. It does patch that. In testing this, the way to get around it would be to edit your keys, then update. Then change your WillowDLC.ini back to saying +NumKeys=1 and then update. You should still have your keys.

@shauwy
If you edited your WillowDLC.ini for the keys, you'll have to change the number of keys back to 1. If you dont, then your game will have an error and wont launch. Try doing that if you did give yourself those keys.

